Body: Update 7: Tokens for the telegram airdrop has been distributed. The signature and the twitter will be sent out soon. Do take note that Timebox failed to hit the softcap. In the event of unable to meet the softcap, dev team can choose to cancel the project and investors will be refunded and bounty participants will not be able to receive any tokens. That is the risk of taking part in alt coin bounty campaign. You risk to gain more, but you also can got nothing for a cancelled project.  However for timebox, the team decided to continue the project and conduct private fund rising. There will be changes to the roadmap. On the good side, the team recognise the effort of the bounty participants, so they will still pay out for twitter and signature campaign.

Author: KesaruWimal
Title: [BOUNTY] TIMEBOX | $250,000 given away| 5 weeks only |üí≤Attractive Signatureüí≤
Body: TimeBox Coin is a general virtual coin for Memory Blockchain Asset Trust Bank. TimeBox users need to pay TimeBox Coin to get service, and miners who support the fragmentation of TimeBox can receive a specific amount of TimeBox Coin as a reward. TimeBox Coin is a decentralized storage network that turns cloud storage into an algorithmic market. The market runs on a blockchain with a native protocol coin  which miners earn by providing storage to clients. Conversely, clients spend TB Coin hiring miners to store or distribute data. As with Bitcoin, TB Coin miners compete to mine blocks with sizable rewards, but TB Coin mining power is proportional to active storage, which directly provides a useful service to clients. This creates a powerful incentive for miners to amass as much storage as they can, and rent it out to clients.

Body: Update 8: TB has been distributed to the signature and twitter participants since Apr-26-2018 UTC. Thanks for all the wonderful participants. As i have mentioned that the softcap is not reached but the team still will continue to push for the project, it may take quite some time for the team to raise the sufficient funds and then focus on the exchanges. This will demand a lot of patient.  I will be locking the thread. Once again, thanks for all the wonderful participants.    Update 7: Tokens for the telegram airdrop has been distributed. The signature and the twitter will be sent out soon. Do take note that Timebox failed to hit the softcap. In the event of unable to meet the softcap, dev team can choose to cancel the project and investors will be refunded and bounty participants will not be able to receive any tokens. That is the risk of taking part in alt coin bounty campaign. You risk to gain more, but you also can got nothing for a cancelled project.  However for timebox, the team decided to continue the project and conduct private fund rising. There will be changes to the roadmap. On the good side, the team recognise the effort of the bounty participants, so they will still pay out for twitter and signature campaign.   Update 6: Data for both the signature and twitter campaign has been submitted to the dev team. I will update when i have their schedule on when the tokens distribution.   Update 5: Signature participants can removed their signature code already. Thanks for the helping timebox to promote.  Flow of event: From Monday 0001 Forum Time the twitter campaign spreadsheet should be completed and you will have 48hrs to check. If there is any changes need to be made. You will have to inform me by pm before Wednesday 2359 Forum Time. The data will be submitted to the dev team on Thursday where changes cant be made anymore.   Update 4: Hi all participants, as i now realise i have made a mistake in the dates of the weekly report, i will honor the wrong dates.  That means the date for week 5 will be Apr 7 to Apr 14, and not Apr 7 to Apr 13 as it should be meant to be.  This applies to both signature and twitter campaign.  Make sure all your weekly report for twitter is post before Apr 14 2359 forum time.     Update 1: Make sure you have checked out the amended dates for each week. Week 1 Mar 10 to Mar 16 Week 2 Mar 17 to Mar 23 Week 3 Mar 24 to Mar 30 Week 4 Mar 31 to Apr 6 Week 5 Apr 7 to Apr 14   Update 2: The signature list has been updated with accepted signature participants. TimeBox leverage blockchain technology with guaranteed delivery service, is the key solution to the needs or pains for everyone. Your best choice for valuable digital assets, TimeBox!  ~~For more Information, refer to our ANN THREAD~~  It is the duty of every individual to check that the entry is recorded correctly. If the data is not entered correctly, immediately pm me so I can do the necessary changes. Otherwise, incomplete information/data will not be rewarded any stakes. Please indicate the following when you pm me - Which Ico Project - Which bounty section of the ICO bounty program that you participated in - Details of the necessary changes - Proof (if any)   Upon hitting the softcap, tokens will be paid out after the end of ICO. Do allow up to a few weeks for the token distribution to happen. Do note that in the event of the softcap is not hit, there will not be any payout.
